premise_source_doc_sentence: The K2 is a 2016 South Korean television series starring Ji Chang-wook , Im Yoon-ah and Song Yoon-ah .
`` Older Sister ''  )  is a 2006 South Korean television series starring Song Yoon-ah and Kim Sung-soo .
Song Yoon-ah  (  Korean : 송윤아 , born June 7 , 1973  )  is a South Korean actress .
